# What do Career Spotlights look like in the curriculum?

#### Career Spotlights provide a connecting thread throughout Synthesize lessons. Each lesson contains the following:

## **An Artist Spotlight**

#### The **Sequencing and Loops Synthesize lessons** (lessons 4 and 8) contain videos for you and your students to watch. Click the images below to watch each video.

<div style="width: 80%; margin: 25px auto; display: flex; gap: 5%;">
  <!-- Video 1: Sequencing -->
  <div style="text-align: center; width: 43%;">
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OrrZPzgWPII" target="_blank">
      <img src="https://images.code.org/e237ecc91f265333140e5db625446295-image-1745279755766.51.59 PM.png" alt="Henny Tha Bizness video thumbnail" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;">
